                            <comment id="12547919" author="stack" created="Mon, 3 Dec 2007 18:05:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Few comment B:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+ Would suggest that you add support for &apos;&lt;del&gt;h|&lt;/del&gt;-help&apos; and fail if folks provide args. that you don&apos;t handle outputting a usage message that includes defaults for port and address&lt;br/&gt;
+ Are the methods getWebAppsPath and getWebAppDir copied from InfoServer?  If so, should we make it so this code refers to them over there?  What would need to be done?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Otherwise patch looks good Bryan.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
